Subject: [PATCH] =?UTF-8?q?feat(rivetta):=20v2=20native=20Plane=20integrat?=
 =?UTF-8?q?ion=20=E2=80=94=20design=20tokens,=20propel=20components?=
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Replace all hardcoded Tailwind colors and custom HTML elements with Plane's
native design system: Pill, Button, IconButton, ModalCore, Popover, and
semantic tokens (bg-layer-*, text-secondary, border-subtle, etc.).

- phase.ts: EPillVariant enum + all tokens replacing raw Tailwind
- phase-badge.tsx: uses Pill component, timeline uses bg-accent-*/bg-layer-3
- phase-controls.tsx: Button/IconButton from @plane/propel, bg-layer-2 container
- handoff-modal.tsx: ModalCore + Button variants replacing fixed overlay div
- phase-chip.tsx (NEW): compact Popover chip in project header, always visible
- tab-navigation-root.tsx: inserts RivettaPhaseChip next to ProjectActionsMenu
- sidebar.tsx: SidebarNavItem + useNavigate replacing custom button
- vault/page.tsx: native layout — border-subtle, bg-layer-2 cards, Input, Button
- create/root.tsx: phase/template fields styled with text-13/accent-subtle tokens
- globals.css: trimmed safelist to only remaining hardcoded colors (pink/orange)

